title: Sunny SIXTEEN
description: Hanabusa Niina, 16 years old. With 'a face that makes her a winner', she is envied by her friends, but has a complex about never being able to decide on anything. One day, armed with an SLR and the advice of former idol and school alumna Mimiri, she awakens to the joy in taking pictures.
author: Watanuki Hiroya
